Description: =======
        pyquote
        =======
        
        Usage
        -----
        
        .. code:: python
        
            >>> share = Share('aapl')
            >>> print(share.get_price())
            143.17
            >>> print(share.get_market_cap())
            751147131800
        
        Methods
        -------
        
        - ``get_name()``
        - ``get_exchange()``
        - ``get_price()``
        - ``get_change()``
        - ``get_percent_change()``
        - ``get_open()``
        - ``get_close()``
        - ``get_avg_volume()``
        - ``get_volume()``
        - ``get_year_high()``
        - ``get_year_low()``
        - ``get_year_change()``
        - ``get_price_earnings_ratio()``
        - ``get_market_cap()``
        
        Terms
